The impact of conventional cost-effectiveness analysis on pricing dynamics in 
the market of new medicines: a proposed countervailing approach.

Capri S(1), Antoñanzas F(2), Levaggi R(3).

Author information:
(1)School of Economics and Management, Cattaneo-LIUC University, Castellanza 
(Varese), Italy.
(2)Department of Economics, University of La Rioja, Logrono, Spain.
(3)Dipartimento di Economia e Management, Università degli Studi di Brescia, 
