Cost-effectiveness of home non-invasive ventilation in patients with persistent 
hypercapnia after an acute exacerbation of COPD in the UK.

Murphy PB(1)(2), Brueggenjuergen B(3), Reinhold T(4), Gu Q(5), Fusfeld L(5), 
Criner G(6), Goss TF(5), Hart N(7)(2).

Author information:
(1)Lane Fox Respiratory Service, Guy's and St Thomas' NHS Foundation Trust, 
