Green Tea Epigallocatechin Gallate Inhibits Preadipocyte Growth via the 
microRNA-let-7a/HMGA2 Signaling Pathway.

Chen WT(1), Yang MJ(2), Tsuei YW(3), Su TC(2), Siao AC(1), Kuo YC(4), Huang 
