(2)Tea Research and Extension Station, Council of Agriculture, Executive Yuan 
Number 324 Chung-Hsing RD., Taoyuan, 326, Taiwan.
(3)Department of Emergency Medicine, Taoyuan Armed Forces General Hospital, 
