The Local Release of Teriparatide Incorporated in 45S5 Bioglass Promotes a 
Beneficial Effect on Osteogenic Cells and Bone Repair in Calvarial Defects in 
Ovariectomized Rats.

de Araújo JCR(1), Sobral Silva LA(1), de Barros Lima VA(1), Bastos Campos TM(2), 
Lisboa Filho PN(3), Okamoto R(4), de Vasconcellos LMR(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Bioscience and Buccal Diagnose, Institute of Science and 
Technology, Sao Paulo State University, UNESP, Sao Paulo 12245-700, SP, Brazil.
(2)Department of Prosthodontics and Periodontology, Bauru School of Dentistry, 
