115. J Mol Diagn. 2023 Mar;25(3):143-155. doi: 10.1016/j.jmoldx.2022.12.003.

Contrived Materials and a Data Set for the Evaluation of Liquid Biopsy Tests: A 
Blood Profiling Atlas in Cancer (BLOODPAC) Community Study.

Hernandez KM(1), Bramlett KS(2), Agius P(3), Baden J(4), Cao R(2), Clement O(5), 
Corner AS(6), Craft J(7), Dean DA 2nd(8), Dry JR(3), Grigaityte K(3), Grossman 
RL(9), Hicks J(10), Higa N(10), Holzer TR(11), Jensen J(12), Johann DJ(13), Katz 
S(14), Kolatkar A(10), Keynton JL(15), Lee JSH(16), Maar D(6), Martini JF(17), 
Meyer CG(18), Roberts PC(17), Ryder M(7), Salvatore L(19), Schageman JJ(2), 
Somiari S(20), Stetson D(21), Stern M(4), Xu L(10), Leiman LC(22).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medicine, University of Chicago, Chicago, Illinois; Center for 
Translational Data Science, University of Chicago, Chicago, Illinois.
(2)Thermo Fisher Scientific, Austin, Texas.
(3)Tempus, Chicago, Illinois.
